Name: Underwater World
About the game: Underwater World - is a colourful 2D platformer with dynamic and hardcore gameplay where you will have to do different levels playing as Plankton. The main aim of the game is simple. You collect definite quantity of items on the level and try not to die. As soon as you do it, you will be opened an entrance to the next level. If you die, don't be sad as you will be able to do the level one more time. You will bump into various enemies and obstacles, go away from them, think of your every step. You will do it! KEY FEATURES: - A pretty graphics - Dinamic gameplay - 15 long and hardcore levels - Unforgettable impressions from the game
